items.title: Piramal Enterprises to delist shares on September 23; shareholders to get 1:1 allotment in Piramal Finance
items.description: PEL had earlier updated investors through stock exchange announcements on September 11 and September 16, 2025.

items.title: GRSE inks $62.4-million contract with Germany's Carsten Rehder for building 4 vessels
items.description: The 120-metre-long and 17-metre-wide vessels will feature battery-assisted hybrid propulsion, improved fuel efficiency, and flexible cargo handling systems

items.title: H-1B visa fee hike likely to hit Indian IT firms by $1 billion: Sandip Agarwal of Sowilo Investment Managers
items.description: Indian visa consultants have raised concerns over US President Donald Trump’s Executive Order that increases the fee companies must pay to sponsor H-1B applicants to $100,000
